{"title":"San Util Design Whirlpool Hip Pack in Stock","link":"https://theradavist.com/san-util-whirlpool-hip-pack-in-stock/","date":1733925964000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-28_b6bb2e8a-5f.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-28_b6bb2e8a-5f.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-28_b6bb2e8a-5f.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-28_b6bb2e8a-5f.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Colorado bag maker <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/san-util-design/\" target=\"_blank\">San Util</a> just announced a new hip pack called the Whirlpool ($135)…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-24_28ed57c5-c5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-24_28ed57c5-c5.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-24_28ed57c5-c5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-24_28ed57c5-c5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>San Util makes some of our staff’s favorite packs. From the mini <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/san-util-designs-covert-v3-hip-pack-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Covert V3 hip bag</a> to the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/san-util-designs-roly-poly-handlebar-bag/\" target=\"_blank\">Roly Poly Handlebar Bag</a>, to the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/san-util-mini-and-light-weight-panniers-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Mini Panniers</a>, this Colorado maker rolls out excellence from his small shop in Winter Park. New to the lineup is the Whirlpool Hip Pack, designed to carry a water bladder or bottle and all your riding essentials for a big day out.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/20230503-dsc03232.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/20230503-dsc03232.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/20230503-dsc03232.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/20230503-dsc03232.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-8.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-8.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilBikepackingBagRIdeShoot-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>It was designed with stability, comfort, and simplicity in mind. The name was picked because the pack is a water-carrying machine and is a roll-top closure, hence, The Whirlpool. Its wings are designed with as much area as possible to help distribute the heavy water load. They are sewn in at two points per wing to give them the flexibility to move to the rider’s body. The daisy chain webbing on the back is the perfect spot to strap a coat, carabiner your coffee mug, or clip some sunscreen. You can also take your sunglasses and put the arms through the webbing if you need a place to let them air out.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-11_3323099c-53.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-11_3323099c-53.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-11_3323099c-53.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/SanUtilNewHipPack-11_3323099c-53.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Made in Winter Park, CO</li>\n<li>3.5 – 5 L design</li>\n<li>10.5″ X 7.5″ X 3.5″</li>\n<li>EPX200 – 335g</li>\n<li>Expandable Design</li>\n<li>Comfortable Wing Design w/ Stretch Pockets</li>\n<li>Malice Clip Attachment</li>\n<li>3 Internal Pockets w/ Key Loop</li>\n<li>Magnet Buckle for Main</li>\n<li>Hydration Bladder Hose Hole</li>\n<li>Compression Straps for Knee Pads or Coat</li>\n<li>Compatible w/ Bottle Holsters and Bladder</li>\n<li>Upgrade Buckle Available</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There’s a lot going on with the Whirlpool, so check out more at <a href=\"https://sanutildesign.com/products/whirlpool-hip-pack-retail?se_activity_id=140984549428&amp;syclid=ctc7hq0aimfs73bkajk0&amp;utm_campaign=All+new+ski+pack+and+a+special+discount+just+for+you+%28And+everyone+else%29_140984549428&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=shopify_email\" target=\"_blank\">San Util</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/san-util-whirlpool-hip-pack-in-stock/\">San Util Design Whirlpool Hip Pack in Stock</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ebb1fa668a683b7c730909233f2b8513ff4ce944d9ea2cb5f9fea44acbfab969","category":"Cycling"}